---
title: Grilled Maple-Mustard Tofu with BBQ Seasoned Potato Wedges and Caesar Dressed Slaw
description: Classic Canadian flavours like maple and mustard are always a winner – and they're delicious when slathered on tofu. Potato wedges get tossed with BBQ seasoning for added smoky goodness.
